data.description: This single-level home is in a fantastic community. The 3-bed, 2-bath Half Mile Lake gem is ready for your individual touches to make it a home. Grab the opportunity to be in one of Greenville's favorite neighborhoods and school zones!  Step inside and you'll find an inviting living area with a cathedral ceiling and gas fireplace. The kitchen has plenty of storage with solid oak cabinets, and there is a separate pantry and laundry area nearby. For a smaller home, this house has a great and efficient layout.  You'll love the spacious primary ensuite with a walk-in shower and two closets. This home has a BRAND NEW roof with architectural shingles, and the HVAC system and garage door were recently installed in 2021.  With the big ticket items already taken care of, you can focus on adding your personal touches. The 2-car garage boasts a separate workshop space with a utility sink, counter, and shelving.  The corner lot on a quiet cul-de-sac provides ample space for outdoor activities and gardening. The backyard features a large, private deck, and a row of trees creates a private space that is already partially fenced in.  This home is in Half Mile Lake, a highly desirable neighborhood known for its annual traditions, swim team, and trick-or-treating. Whether it's at a block party, holiday celebrations, or summer days with food trucks by the community pool, you'll quickly get to know your neighbors. Half Mile Lake even has its own Christmas parade each year! This home is convenient to everything, with Paris Mountain State Park just 4 minutes up State Park Road. It's only 12 minutes to Downtown Greenville, 20 minutes to Greer, 20 minutes to Woodruff Rd shopping, and 12 minutes to Traveler's Rest.  Don't miss out on this opportunity to make this lovely house your new home. Schedule a viewing today and start living your best life in this delightful neighborhood.
